{
  "stem": "9091.3",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And there was-- also, there was a Polish hospital, already from the Polish government, that she opened in Samarkand.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So she was put there, in that hospital.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And after she recovered, she came to visit us.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And this how we found out where she disappeared, how she disappeared.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And in that hospital, she stayed, just-- she worked there, just to have a meal a day and somewhere to put her head down, you know?",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "What was it like for you at the orphanage?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, it was some antisemitism that we-- that we countered there.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We had to be with every day in the-- every day in the morning, we had to stand together, with all Polish children.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They used to do their prayers.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we had to be there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They didn't force us to pray.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But we had to stay with-- there, in the same room, and [? yeah. ?] And this is how I learned all the-- all the prayer, all the Polish prayer, all the Catholic prayers.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we stayed for a while in that orphanage.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I guess it wasn't more than some months, till they told us that we are leaving Russia for Palestine.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, there was one huge hole-- huge hole-- where-- and I don't know if they were beds.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I-- I think maybe they were beds, one beside the other-- one huge hole, where all the children were sleeping, one-- one beside the other.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I think they were over-- I think 150 children in that orphanage.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We were fed-- I mean, not overfed, but you know.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Under those conditions, it was like heaven, you know.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And-- and the teachers were very nice-- very nice.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I remember I loved our taker-- caretakers.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They liked me.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And-- and we were generally happy there, you know.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
